people by their appearance!

01:45:17.650 --> 01:45:20.585
- We have a rabbi!
- We have a rabbi!

01:45:25.658 --> 01:45:28.320
Excuse me, Rabbi, please forgive me.

01:45:28.728 --> 01:45:31.253
