please make a little room here.

01:45:51.350 --> 01:45:53.648
<i>Thank you. I'm so
sorry to spoil your...</i>

01:45:53.720 --> 01:45:56.985
Bartender, drinks for all my friends.

01:45:57.056 --> 01:45:59.456
